snippet.title: BattleTabs Development Update 01
snippet.description:
Big changes are coming to BattleTabs! We are adding new ships, new monsters, abilities, and the concept of fleets, alongside some UI updates to make room for these new changes. Watch the video for a quick summary of what's coming soon!

Play BattleTabs for free: https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/battle-tabs/mjcklhnhfiepmofggcoegkmkokbljmjd

Support BattleTabs: https://ko-fi.com/battletabs
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/BattleTabsGame/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/BattleTabs
